WEBVTT

01:44.400 --> 01:47.480
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:51.960 --> 01:53.920
The Crown Prince's son
is still alive, correct?

01:54.760 --> 01:55.720
Yes.

01:56.680 --> 01:57.640
He now lives

01:58.640 --> 01:59.800
as Prince Changxin's eldest son.

01:59.880 --> 02:01.920
Sui Yuanhuai.

02:03.280 --> 02:06.360
Who gave you permission
to light a fire in this courtyard?

02:07.040 --> 02:08.840
Are your eyes useless?

02:10.320 --> 02:12.080
Dig her eyes out.

02:12.160 --> 02:13.560
Spare me, Master!

02:13.640 --> 02:14.480
Get out!

02:16.440 --> 02:17.680
Yes, madam.

02:29.160 --> 02:30.080
You dared strike me?

02:30.920 --> 02:32.640
Over a lowly servant?

02:33.320 --> 02:34.440
In your eyes,

02:34.520 --> 02:36.440
am I worth less than a slave?

02:37.320 --> 02:39.440
I just didn't want
more blood on your hands.

02:39.520 --> 02:41.480
She is a pitiful soul. And so are you.

02:46.000 --> 02:47.720
After the Jinzhou tragedy,

02:47.800 --> 02:51.040
Princess Changxin brought her
eldest son, Sui Yuanhuai, into the palace

02:52.080 --> 02:53.800
to accompany the widowed Crown Princess.

02:54.600 --> 02:57.040
But then a fire broke out
in the Eastern Palace.

02:57.640 --> 03:00.560
The Crown Princess
and her son both perished

03:00.640 --> 03:01.640
in that blaze.

03:02.760 --> 03:05.640
Prince Changxin's eldest son
was badly burned.

03:06.200 --> 03:08.320
After that, he vanished from public life.

03:11.240 --> 03:13.280
So the real Sui Yuanhuai…

03:13.360 --> 03:15.760
Most likely died in that fire
at the Eastern Palace

03:17.240 --> 03:19.120
17 years ago.

03:23.760 --> 03:25.280
You call me pitiful?

03:26.720 --> 03:27.760
Are you not?

03:28.360 --> 03:30.760
You are selfish, cruel,

03:30.840 --> 03:32.840
vicious, and unpredictable.

03:32.920 --> 03:35.040
Everyone who serves you
lives in constant fear.

03:35.120 --> 03:36.400
One misstep and they die.

03:37.280 --> 03:38.880
All of this is just your disguise.

03:39.680 --> 03:41.680
You are hiding your fear.

03:44.160 --> 03:46.000
You are the one to be pitied.

03:50.600 --> 03:51.960
You call me pitiful too.

03:53.640 --> 03:54.480
That year,

03:55.920 --> 03:57.440
when my mother pushed me into the brazier,

03:59.920 --> 04:01.280
she said the same thing.

04:02.560 --> 04:03.880
Mother!

04:03.960 --> 04:05.320
Min.

04:06.240 --> 04:07.080
Mother!

04:07.160 --> 04:10.000
This is the only way you can survive.

04:10.080 --> 04:11.520
Mother!

04:14.920 --> 04:16.519
‎VIRTUOUS AND GRACIOUS

04:19.519 --> 04:20.600
Min.

04:21.880 --> 04:22.880
You must live.

04:32.840 --> 04:34.240
So all these years,

04:35.440 --> 04:37.840
Prince Changxin never suspected

04:37.920 --> 04:39.840
his eldest son had been replaced.

04:41.280 --> 04:42.360
He always said

04:43.200 --> 04:44.840
the eldest son never grew close to him.

04:46.200 --> 04:48.520
But what father would doubt his own child?

04:49.440 --> 04:52.240
After the burns, our Master changed a lot.

04:52.320 --> 04:53.680
That seemed only natural.

04:54.880 --> 04:56.880
Yet a father's instinct

04:57.760 --> 04:59.960
made him dislike the boy from the start.

05:01.000 --> 05:02.240
In the end, the heir's title

05:02.320 --> 05:03.960
went to the second son, Sui Yuanqing.

05:05.200 --> 05:06.200
Which means

05:07.720 --> 05:09.720
Sui Yuanqing's appearance in Lin'an

05:10.880 --> 05:13.120
was part of Qi Min's plan?

05:14.160 --> 05:16.400
The Crown Prince's son, Qi Min,
knew you were in Lin'an.

05:16.480 --> 05:18.080
He wanted to use your hand

05:18.160 --> 05:19.680
to get rid of Sui Yuanqing.

05:20.440 --> 05:22.520
At the time,
the Chongzhou army was still strong.

05:22.600 --> 05:24.160
If they had taken Jizhou,

05:24.240 --> 05:26.800
they could have marched south
straight into the imperial palace.

05:26.880 --> 05:28.640
The emperor could have
been forced to abdicate.

05:29.240 --> 05:30.600
But Sui Yuanqing is the rightful heir.

05:30.680 --> 05:32.640
If the throne changed hands,
it would be his.

05:33.320 --> 05:34.240
That is why

05:35.120 --> 05:38.560
Qi Min was determined to see him dead.

05:39.160 --> 05:41.760
My mother spent her entire life
scheming for the Eastern Palace.

05:43.040 --> 05:44.640
Yet in the end she met a tragic fate.

05:45.800 --> 05:49.200
Qi Min even sought to kill his own son.

05:52.040 --> 05:54.600
Crown Prince Chengde,
renowned for loyalty and righteousness,

05:55.440 --> 05:56.560
yet his son became a usurper

05:57.080 --> 05:59.240
who stole another man's place.

06:00.440 --> 06:02.120
Cold-blooded and ruthless.

06:03.560 --> 06:05.360
What strange fate Lin'an holds.

06:06.120 --> 06:07.320
First it sheltered Marquis Wu'an.

06:07.400 --> 06:08.480
Now it hides
the Eastern Palace's last heir.

06:10.040 --> 06:11.640
And Yu Qianqian…

06:11.720 --> 06:13.120
She is no ordinary either, is she?

06:14.800 --> 06:17.360
The Marquis and Mr. Gongsun
are both correct.

06:18.760 --> 06:20.440
The proprietress of Yixiang Restaurant

06:21.160 --> 06:22.960
is the concubine who fled from Qi Min.

06:27.840 --> 06:28.840
Yu Bao'er

06:29.760 --> 06:31.000
is the imperial great grandson.

06:40.440 --> 06:41.560
You have no idea

06:42.280 --> 06:44.720
what torment and suffering
I endured to survive

06:45.960 --> 06:47.480
until today.

06:49.040 --> 06:50.800
And so you pass that suffering

06:51.720 --> 06:53.440
onto others?

06:54.480 --> 06:57.720
I was born
the most exalted son under heaven.

07:00.080 --> 07:01.880
The throne of Dayin

07:02.520 --> 07:04.200
should have been mine.

07:04.920 --> 07:05.960
And yet now,

07:07.200 --> 07:10.040
I must live on under a revolting identity,

07:10.560 --> 07:12.200
barely clinging to life.

07:13.440 --> 07:17.160
If Qi Min ever takes the throne,

07:17.240 --> 07:19.000
the people will suffer greatly.

07:20.400 --> 07:21.880
Marquis, you are a hero without equal.

07:22.720 --> 07:24.040
If you were willing to support

07:24.720 --> 07:26.560
the imperial great grandson
in claiming the throne,

07:27.560 --> 07:29.800
it would be a blessing
for the people of the realm.

07:34.920 --> 07:36.400
Seventeen years ago,

07:36.480 --> 07:37.600
the Jinzhou massacre.

07:38.680 --> 07:39.920
How much do you know?

07:40.560 --> 07:42.120
Not much.

07:42.800 --> 07:43.720
But Qi Min

07:44.600 --> 07:46.160
may know the truth.

07:48.080 --> 07:49.040
Crown Prince Chengde,

07:49.760 --> 07:52.280
who died in Jinzhou,

07:54.160 --> 07:55.480
was your father.

08:01.520 --> 08:02.440
Yes.

08:04.760 --> 08:05.720
I set all this up

08:06.320 --> 08:08.240
to force Prince Changxin into rebellion.

08:08.320 --> 08:09.840
Only then could I seize back

08:10.400 --> 08:13.040
the realm that rightfully mine.

08:13.120 --> 08:14.800
Wei Yan

08:15.440 --> 08:18.320
and everyone who destroyed my family

08:19.000 --> 08:20.760
must all die.

08:26.520 --> 08:28.880
But how can you possibly defeat

08:30.600 --> 08:32.000
Wei Yan and Marquis Wu'an?

08:34.559 --> 08:35.919
Even if I lose,

08:36.720 --> 08:38.679
I'll make sure Xie, Wei,

08:38.760 --> 08:40.640
and Prince Changxin all suffer in pain.

08:42.120 --> 08:43.799
Even if I were to die,

08:44.640 --> 08:47.440
others would die in my place.

08:49.560 --> 08:50.760
What do you mean?

08:54.360 --> 08:56.640
I have leverage over Prince Changxin.

09:00.000 --> 09:01.360
This tiger tally is the proof

09:02.160 --> 09:04.360
of what truly happened
in the Jinzhou massacre.

09:06.600 --> 09:07.720
This tally does not match.

09:07.800 --> 09:08.960
It is fake.

09:09.520 --> 09:11.840
Your Highness, the tiger tally is genuine.

09:11.920 --> 09:13.680
Please dispatch the troops at once.

09:13.760 --> 09:16.320
Crown Prince Chengde and General Xie
cannot hold out much longer.

09:16.400 --> 09:17.760
Jinzhou is about to fall!

09:24.360 --> 09:26.120
Why tell me all this?

09:27.880 --> 09:29.560
Are you not afraid I might betray you?

09:32.560 --> 09:34.040
Because I know

09:34.680 --> 09:36.200
you are my woman.

09:37.240 --> 09:39.200
You would never betray me.

10:09.000 --> 10:09.840
Up you go.

10:12.480 --> 10:13.960
Uncle Yan,

10:14.480 --> 10:16.360
I miss my mother very much.

10:17.000 --> 10:18.440
But I know

10:18.520 --> 10:20.280
now is not the time to get her out.

10:22.080 --> 10:22.920
Do not worry.

10:23.560 --> 10:25.280
I have sent people to look for her.

10:25.360 --> 10:26.440
We will find her.

10:26.520 --> 10:28.040
Once I do,

10:28.120 --> 10:31.400
I will send you to reunite with Ning.
How does that sound?

10:32.000 --> 10:34.160
Changning made it safely back to Jizhou?

10:35.240 --> 10:36.120
What about Aunt Fan?

10:38.880 --> 10:40.840
They are both doing well.

10:42.160 --> 10:43.160
Do not worry.

10:43.240 --> 10:45.160
They will return safely to Lin'an.

10:47.000 --> 10:47.840
Off you go.

10:54.880 --> 10:55.720
Marquis,

10:56.360 --> 10:57.880
we must depart for Lucheng at once.

10:59.120 --> 11:01.520
Prince Changxin's forces
will likely reach Lucheng soon.

11:03.840 --> 11:05.160
Pass the order.

11:05.240 --> 11:08.040
-Break camp. We march for Lucheng.
-Yes, Marquis.

11:38.920 --> 11:39.800
Someone!

11:40.520 --> 11:41.360
Go find the madam.

11:42.360 --> 11:44.240
Master, the madam is gone.

11:44.320 --> 11:46.800
I was just about to report it.

11:46.880 --> 11:48.360
But we could not wake you.

11:54.160 --> 11:55.560
That wretched woman.

11:56.680 --> 11:58.680
She dared not poison me to death,

11:58.760 --> 12:00.440
but who knows what drug she gave me.

12:05.880 --> 12:09.200
BOUNDARY OF LUCHENG, JIZHOU PREFECTURE

12:09.280 --> 12:10.240
Lucheng.

12:12.560 --> 12:14.360
Beyond here is Lucheng territory.

12:17.160 --> 12:18.320
Someone's there.

12:23.520 --> 12:24.600
Qian!

12:25.280 --> 12:26.440
Changyu!

12:35.040 --> 12:35.920
Changyu.

12:36.480 --> 12:37.960
How did you get out?

12:38.040 --> 12:39.360
We were about to go look for you.

12:39.440 --> 12:41.080
As if I'd sit there and wait to die.

12:42.160 --> 12:44.040
We have to go.
Qi Min will be here any moment.

12:55.960 --> 12:57.080
Trying to run?

12:58.000 --> 12:59.040
Where can you go?

12:59.800 --> 13:00.920
Fan Changyu.

13:01.000 --> 13:02.760
You actually managed to track me here.

13:02.840 --> 13:03.920
Foolish perhaps,

13:04.440 --> 13:05.880
but I admire your courage.

13:06.560 --> 13:09.280
Kill them all. Leave only the madam alive.

13:22.800 --> 13:24.080
He Jingyuan.

13:26.800 --> 13:28.360
General Xie Qi. How did you find me?

13:28.440 --> 13:30.360
The Marquis ordered me
to protect you in secret.

13:30.440 --> 13:32.160
He feared danger when you reached Lucheng.

13:32.240 --> 13:34.480
So he asked General He
to come meet us here.

13:35.480 --> 13:36.480
Drop your weapons.

13:37.080 --> 13:38.280
Surrender now!

13:39.440 --> 13:40.600
He Jingyuan,

13:41.120 --> 13:42.760
you think I would fear you?

13:45.760 --> 13:48.800
Sui Yuanhuai, do you truly think
you can fight ten men alone?

13:51.320 --> 13:52.880
If you want her alive,

13:52.960 --> 13:54.960
then you will have to kill me first.

13:57.240 --> 13:59.720
Withdraw now,
or I will kill myself right here.

14:08.400 --> 14:09.240
Fall back!

14:16.040 --> 14:17.960
It is all right now. Everything is fine.

14:21.840 --> 14:22.680
Changyu.

14:23.280 --> 14:24.920
I thought I would never see you again.

14:25.920 --> 14:27.880
Every day, I was thinking
of how to escape.

14:28.440 --> 14:29.680
I never thought I'd succeed.

14:30.320 --> 14:31.760
You are incredible.

14:32.480 --> 14:33.320
Where is Bao'er?

14:34.760 --> 14:36.280
Bao'er was taken away by Nanny Lan.

14:37.360 --> 14:38.640
But Nanny Lan has already…

14:41.240 --> 14:44.240
General, the guards around Sui Yuanhuai
are all elite fighters.

14:44.320 --> 14:47.120
Even though we had the numbers,
we could not gain the upper hand.

14:47.200 --> 14:50.320
The Chongzhou troops who came
to support them covered their retreat.

14:50.920 --> 14:52.400
That man is cunning.

14:53.800 --> 14:55.960
He must have left himself a way out.

14:57.160 --> 14:59.040
As for Bao'er's whereabouts now,

14:59.120 --> 15:00.040
I truly do not know.

15:02.280 --> 15:04.000
Bao'er has always been fortunate.

15:04.080 --> 15:05.320
He will be safe.

15:15.160 --> 15:16.880
Lucheng lies just ahead.

15:16.960 --> 15:18.680
Since we have come this far,

15:18.760 --> 15:20.040
we can discuss the rest

15:20.760 --> 15:22.640
once we return to Lucheng.

15:25.160 --> 15:26.720
Thank you for your help, General He.

15:27.600 --> 15:29.800
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

15:29.880 --> 15:32.720
HE, JIZHOU YAMEN

15:44.600 --> 15:45.600
General.

15:48.160 --> 15:49.400
Changyu.

15:55.800 --> 15:56.640
My respects, General.

15:57.600 --> 15:59.000
Thank you for saving us yesterday.

15:59.080 --> 16:01.000
No need for thanks.

16:01.640 --> 16:03.040
The entire army is talking about it.

16:03.120 --> 16:05.760
They say you killed Shi Hu
with three hammer blows.

16:05.840 --> 16:06.680
Is that true?

16:08.080 --> 16:08.920
Two blows.

16:10.920 --> 16:12.680
‎HALL OF LETTERS

16:12.760 --> 16:14.440
I have always been fond of martial arts.

16:14.520 --> 16:16.920
Would you spar with me for a few moves?

16:17.520 --> 16:19.200
My skills are nothing impressive.

16:19.280 --> 16:20.680
How could they possibly
compare with yours?

16:20.760 --> 16:22.480
Whether they can or not,

16:22.560 --> 16:24.840
we will find out soon enough.

16:26.920 --> 16:28.000
Come.

16:29.760 --> 16:31.720
Give it everything you have.
Do not hold back.

17:20.240 --> 17:22.480
‎LOYAL AND RESOLUTE

17:22.560 --> 17:27.240
SEVENTEEN YEARS AGO

17:52.680 --> 17:54.960
Do you know where the weakness was

17:55.040 --> 17:56.160
in that last move?

17:58.240 --> 17:59.440
Please enlighten me.

18:02.240 --> 18:03.160
You have practiced

18:03.240 --> 18:05.960
the skill pattern for many years.

18:06.040 --> 18:07.560
It's become rigid.

18:07.640 --> 18:10.640
You complete one move,
then follow with the next.

18:10.720 --> 18:12.600
But on the battlefield,

18:12.680 --> 18:15.520
an enemy's attacks shift in an instant.

18:15.600 --> 18:18.080
If one strike fails,
you must change immediately.

18:18.160 --> 18:19.960
Predictable patterns are easily read.

18:20.040 --> 18:22.440
Once they see through you,
you lose your composure.

18:26.320 --> 18:27.480
Thank you for the guidance.

18:28.800 --> 18:31.280
But this technique
was taught to me by my father.

18:31.360 --> 18:34.160
He never showed his skills
in front of outsiders.

18:35.320 --> 18:36.520
So, how is it

18:36.600 --> 18:38.120
that you know it so well

18:38.200 --> 18:39.640
and can counter every move?

18:42.920 --> 18:44.280
Your father and I

18:45.360 --> 18:46.520
were old friends.

18:54.120 --> 18:55.120
Jingyuan,

18:55.200 --> 18:56.800
your spear skills have improved a lot.

18:56.880 --> 18:58.440
You are no less formidable than before.

18:59.200 --> 19:00.360
Any disciple for your spear?

19:01.080 --> 19:04.920
Qilin, are you mocking me again
for being a lonely bachelor?

19:05.000 --> 19:06.760
How could I possibly compare with you?

19:06.840 --> 19:08.480
A virtuous wife and a dutiful daughter.

19:08.560 --> 19:10.680
Are you planning
to pass your blade technique

19:10.760 --> 19:12.440
to that little girl of yours?

19:12.520 --> 19:15.000
Whether that girl
inherits my blade technique

19:15.080 --> 19:15.960
remains to be seen.

19:16.040 --> 19:17.040
But

19:17.120 --> 19:18.720
the way she runs around,

19:18.800 --> 19:20.280
so bold and fiery,

19:20.360 --> 19:21.680
she carries my spirit already.

19:22.280 --> 19:23.760
She is like you already?

19:27.600 --> 19:28.920
That is terrible news.

19:29.000 --> 19:31.280
If she turns out like you,
how will she ever find a husband?

19:32.960 --> 19:35.200
She takes after her mother.
Beautiful as can be.

19:36.600 --> 19:38.080
But her bones and build take after me.

19:38.760 --> 19:41.240
If she truly inherits my blade technique,

19:41.320 --> 19:44.560
then in this world,
there will be no man worthy of her.

19:46.040 --> 19:48.600
My father never mentioned any of this.

19:49.240 --> 19:52.480
And he was just a butcher in Lin'an.

19:53.040 --> 19:55.080
How could he possibly
have been friends with a general?

19:55.160 --> 19:57.040
It is a long story.

19:58.320 --> 20:00.120
Once the siege of Lucheng is lifted,

20:01.240 --> 20:02.840
I will tell you everything.

20:08.480 --> 20:09.560
General.

20:09.640 --> 20:11.920
Our army has never had a female officer.

20:12.000 --> 20:13.240
So I thought

20:13.320 --> 20:15.640
the standard armor might not fit you well.

20:15.720 --> 20:19.200
I had this armor specially made for you.

20:20.120 --> 20:21.480
May it accompany you

20:21.560 --> 20:23.600
as you earn glory and win great victories.

20:24.480 --> 20:25.880
Thank you, General.

20:28.760 --> 20:30.600
The last time I gifted someone armor

20:31.640 --> 20:33.920
was nearly 30 years ago.

20:35.040 --> 20:36.240
Sadly,

20:37.080 --> 20:38.720
that man is no longer with us.

20:42.800 --> 20:43.920
Your old friend

20:44.000 --> 20:45.320
must have been a hero

20:45.400 --> 20:46.920
who died on the battlefield.

20:50.000 --> 20:52.200
Though he did not fall

20:52.280 --> 20:54.720
amid flying sand and clashing blades,

20:55.320 --> 20:58.280
he stopped an unjust army.

20:58.880 --> 21:01.040
For the sake of the people under heaven,

21:01.120 --> 21:02.920
he sacrificed himself.

21:04.360 --> 21:05.560
In the end,

21:06.800 --> 21:09.200
all that remained were the bones
of a loyal man.

21:13.040 --> 21:14.440
My father once said

21:15.040 --> 21:16.160
everyone must die someday.

21:16.800 --> 21:18.840
But if your life
can bring some good to the living,

21:19.600 --> 21:21.120
then it was not lived in vain.

21:22.960 --> 21:25.000
Please do not grieve too deeply,

21:25.080 --> 21:25.920
General.

21:31.880 --> 21:34.080
I heard Teacher was sparring
with the heroine who killed Shi Hu.

21:34.680 --> 21:36.680
I rushed over,
hoping to learn a thing or two.

21:37.840 --> 21:39.080
Menkan.

21:39.640 --> 21:41.480
I knew it was you
the moment I heard your voice.

21:42.240 --> 21:43.560
I had a feeling it was you.

21:45.240 --> 21:47.280
So? Finished already?

21:47.800 --> 21:49.120
Who won?

21:49.720 --> 21:50.720
Since when

21:50.800 --> 21:53.320
did you start calling yourself Menkan?

21:55.280 --> 21:58.280
Sir, please don't laugh at me.
Wenkan, Menkan, that's both me.

21:58.360 --> 21:59.600
It is merely a name.

22:01.360 --> 22:03.040
Did I say something wrong?

22:04.800 --> 22:06.920
Call me whatever you like. I do not mind.

22:09.920 --> 22:11.320
Li Huai'an.

22:11.400 --> 22:12.520
Li Menkan.

22:12.600 --> 22:13.800
Commandant Li.

22:14.320 --> 22:15.920
Scholars really do have so many names.

22:17.480 --> 22:19.680
My adoptive father just gave me
a courtesy name too.

22:20.520 --> 22:21.480
You mean Grand Tutor Tao?

22:23.160 --> 22:24.240
Grand Tutor Tao?

22:25.480 --> 22:27.760
Since when did he become
your adoptive father?

22:28.600 --> 22:29.800
Just recently.

22:29.880 --> 22:31.040
He even gave me a courtesy name.

22:31.120 --> 22:32.120
It is…

22:33.520 --> 22:34.720
"Shanjun".

22:34.800 --> 22:35.800
Which means tigress.

22:35.880 --> 22:38.280
From now on,
everyone can call me Tiger Fan.

22:41.760 --> 22:43.480
Have you been settling in well
in the camp?

22:43.560 --> 22:45.240
I never expected you to be so formidable.

22:45.320 --> 22:46.840
You have earned merit again and again.

22:47.360 --> 22:49.120
You might even outshine
Marquis Wu'an someday.

22:49.840 --> 22:51.080
He is coming to Lucheng too?

22:53.040 --> 22:54.760
It's army business, so I do know.

22:55.360 --> 22:58.400
Xie Zheng has been avoiding
the enemy's scouts and interference.

22:58.920 --> 23:00.440
He likely took a longer route.

23:00.520 --> 23:02.040
But he should arrive in a few days.

23:03.080 --> 23:04.920
Earlier, General He told me

23:05.440 --> 23:07.040
that he and my father were old friends.

23:07.880 --> 23:09.720
Do you know anything about that?

23:12.120 --> 23:13.200
I wanted to ask more,

23:13.720 --> 23:15.120
but he would not say much.

23:15.760 --> 23:17.240
My grandfather once told me

23:17.760 --> 23:20.400
that my father only survived in Lin'an

23:20.480 --> 23:22.120
by living under the name Fan Erniu.

23:22.200 --> 23:24.320
But the Jizhou records clearly stated

23:24.400 --> 23:26.760
that my father was just a butcher
killed by bandits.

23:29.640 --> 23:31.200
Why do I feel

23:31.280 --> 23:32.960
as if everyone is lying to me,

23:33.840 --> 23:35.240
yet everything they say

23:37.880 --> 23:39.760
also sounds true?

23:42.200 --> 23:44.280
If Master He did not
wish to go into detail,

23:44.360 --> 23:45.840
he must have his reasons.

23:47.360 --> 23:49.120
But the fact that he called
your father a friend

23:49.200 --> 23:50.360
is proof enough

23:50.440 --> 23:52.960
that your father must have been
a remarkable man.

23:57.000 --> 23:59.400
Hearing that from you
makes me feel better.

24:03.840 --> 24:05.120
Lucheng is a beautiful place.

24:06.520 --> 24:08.920
Do you think it will soon
end up like Lin'an,

24:09.000 --> 24:10.400
consumed by war?

24:12.960 --> 24:14.360
It's time for you to return to Lin'an.

24:15.200 --> 24:17.360
Changning and Mrs. Zhao
are waiting for you at home.

24:17.440 --> 24:18.400
I can go home?

24:18.480 --> 24:20.560
I'll have someone escort you out
in a few days.

24:22.920 --> 24:24.040
All right.

24:24.120 --> 24:25.480
I observed the stars tonight.

24:25.560 --> 24:26.560
The Martial Star has dimmed.

24:26.640 --> 24:27.560
The Breaking Star drags its shadow.

24:27.640 --> 24:29.040
The omens over Lucheng

24:29.120 --> 24:31.000
foretell bloodshed within three days.

24:32.440 --> 24:34.360
We should first launch a feint.

24:34.960 --> 24:36.640
Draw out the enemy's main force.

24:36.720 --> 24:40.080
Then finish with a final move
and lure them straight into the trap.

24:42.080 --> 24:43.560
The omens may say so,

24:44.080 --> 24:45.480
but in my view,

24:45.560 --> 24:46.960
we should gather all our strength

24:47.040 --> 24:48.040
and strike at the heart.

24:48.920 --> 24:50.280
Take down Prince Changxin.

24:55.120 --> 24:56.960
As expected of you, Xie Jiuheng.

24:57.040 --> 24:58.840
Straight to the point.

24:58.920 --> 25:00.480
Others might have the thought,

25:00.560 --> 25:01.920
but not the nerve.

25:03.200 --> 25:04.600
Shi Yue might suspect it,

25:04.680 --> 25:05.720
but he'd never expect it.

25:06.560 --> 25:09.720
The problem is, this plan
would leave Lucheng's gates wide open.

25:11.000 --> 25:13.280
The city may not hold.

25:13.880 --> 25:14.960
Go inform General He.

25:25.880 --> 25:28.240
I have to say, the fish here are huge.

25:28.320 --> 25:30.960
Right? Big ones. Here,

25:31.480 --> 25:33.080
throw in some herbs
to cut the fishy smell.

25:34.120 --> 25:35.880
You asking for a beating?

25:36.720 --> 25:37.560
Father,

25:37.640 --> 25:39.760
-how did you know we were here?
-Let it roast a bit first.

25:40.920 --> 25:45.440
Naturally, I came to wait
for the fish to bite.

25:49.120 --> 25:50.680
Did you come to ask me

25:51.280 --> 25:52.880
whether I still want to stay in the army?

25:54.760 --> 25:56.160
The way you say that,

25:56.240 --> 25:57.840
does it mean you regret it?

25:57.920 --> 26:00.000
Do you want this old man to teach you

26:00.080 --> 26:02.360
how to stand against 10,000
on the battlefield?

26:06.080 --> 26:07.040
Yes.

26:09.120 --> 26:10.120
And no.

26:12.360 --> 26:14.240
What kind of answer is that?

26:14.320 --> 26:16.240
Hopeless child.

26:17.960 --> 26:18.840
Father,

26:19.720 --> 26:21.600
it is not that I refuse
to stay in the army.

26:22.880 --> 26:24.120
I just do not want

26:25.840 --> 26:27.320
to lead troops into battle anymore.

26:28.560 --> 26:30.640
I do not want to watch people
die before my eyes.

26:32.760 --> 26:34.640
Changyu just wants to go back to Lin'an

26:34.720 --> 26:36.240
and live like an ordinary person.

26:36.840 --> 26:38.600
-Why are you pushing her?
-Exactly.

26:40.840 --> 26:43.040
All of you are kind-hearted people.

26:44.040 --> 26:47.440
But that is only small kindness.

26:48.000 --> 26:52.280
When the nest is overturned,
how can any egg remain unbroken?

26:52.360 --> 26:54.200
The massacre at Lin'an

26:54.280 --> 26:56.320
is proof enough.

26:59.400 --> 27:00.920
When Prince Changxin rebels

27:01.920 --> 27:03.240
and marches south,

27:03.320 --> 27:04.800
he kills.

27:04.880 --> 27:07.800
When the imperial army
moves to suppress him,

27:07.880 --> 27:09.280
they kill as well.

27:10.000 --> 27:11.080
Changyu,

27:11.160 --> 27:12.440
think about it carefully.

27:12.520 --> 27:15.760
What is the difference between the two?

27:20.440 --> 27:21.600
All I know

27:22.160 --> 27:23.640
is the soldiers I killed

27:24.800 --> 27:27.560
might have been just like us
before all these.

27:28.480 --> 27:30.680
Just ordinary folks
who were forced onto the battlefield.

27:34.280 --> 27:35.960
Once war begins,

27:36.040 --> 27:39.840
what difference is there
between soldiers and commoners?

27:41.280 --> 27:44.280
War drains the state's strength.

27:44.360 --> 27:46.520
The cost of supporting one soldier

27:46.600 --> 27:48.920
comes from the labor of ten civilians.

27:49.000 --> 27:51.040
The longer the war drags on,

27:51.120 --> 27:53.280
the harder life becomes for the people.

27:54.200 --> 27:55.920
Starving bodies line the roads.

27:56.000 --> 27:58.000
Refugees wander from place to place.

27:58.080 --> 27:59.200
That is why it is said,

27:59.280 --> 28:01.320
in war, victory matters, not duration.

28:01.840 --> 28:04.640
If a war can be ended quickly
with the fewest casualties,

28:05.240 --> 28:06.640
then even those who kill

28:07.280 --> 28:10.240
may still be doing the greater good.

28:24.040 --> 28:25.720
Take this to defend yourself.

28:26.400 --> 28:28.240
Your butcher's knife was already worn out.

28:28.840 --> 28:30.520
So I melted it down and reforged it

28:31.400 --> 28:32.720
into these twin blades.

28:33.600 --> 28:35.280
I have never properly
given you a gift before.

28:35.880 --> 28:38.000
These blades suit you perfectly.

28:39.960 --> 28:41.480
You did give me something before.

28:42.600 --> 28:44.840
The bracers you gave me were very nice.

28:47.440 --> 28:48.880
Why do I smell blood?

28:55.360 --> 28:57.240
-You are hurt.
-No.

28:57.320 --> 28:59.080
Just an old injury.

28:59.160 --> 29:01.320
Liar. You were perfectly fine
a few days ago.

29:01.400 --> 29:02.840
Why would it flare up today?

29:02.920 --> 29:03.960
Let me see.

29:04.040 --> 29:05.200
They are only small wounds.

29:05.280 --> 29:06.960
If you won't let me see, leave.

29:15.680 --> 29:16.520
How did you get hurt?

29:17.560 --> 29:18.480
Who did this to you?

29:20.960 --> 29:21.920
I used my blood…

29:23.600 --> 29:24.440
to consecrate it.

29:24.520 --> 29:25.560
Are you out of your mind?

29:41.040 --> 29:42.680
You have read too many storybooks.

29:43.400 --> 29:44.840
You think I'd be moved to tears?

29:47.560 --> 29:48.920
If you ever do that again,

29:49.000 --> 29:51.920
I will buy a hundred blades
for you to bleed on.

29:53.400 --> 29:54.880
If your arm runs out, use your backside.

30:07.840 --> 30:08.840
Changyu,

30:08.920 --> 30:11.320
do you remember
when we were at the Wu River camp,

30:11.400 --> 30:14.160
and I told you to hunt down
those three scouts?

30:14.240 --> 30:16.720
If you had shown mercy

30:16.800 --> 30:18.960
and let them go,

30:19.040 --> 30:23.080
then the one to suffer
would have been Lucheng.

30:24.120 --> 30:28.200
And the dead would have been far more
than just one or a few.

30:39.720 --> 30:40.800
I understand now.

30:40.880 --> 30:41.920
Thank you for the guidance.

30:58.360 --> 30:59.520
Madam,

30:59.600 --> 31:00.880
the falcon brought a message.

31:00.960 --> 31:02.240
The Marquis has found Yu Bao'er

31:02.320 --> 31:03.560
and sent him to Lin'an.

31:05.200 --> 31:06.160
That is wonderful.

31:06.840 --> 31:09.600
Now Qian can return to Lin'an
and reunite with Bao'er.

31:11.320 --> 31:12.480
We should pack as well.

31:12.560 --> 31:13.840
We leave tomorrow morning.

31:13.920 --> 31:14.760
Yes.

31:15.880 --> 31:17.960
I just paid a visit to General He.

31:18.040 --> 31:20.440
I heard that you and Mrs. Fan
will soon return to Lin'an.

31:21.000 --> 31:22.200
So I came to see you.

31:24.320 --> 31:25.760
Changyu already told me.

31:26.280 --> 31:28.720
Thank you, and the Marquis,
for saving Bao'er.

31:29.320 --> 31:30.480
I'm deeply grateful.

31:32.080 --> 31:34.000
-Please allow me to bow.
-No, no.

31:34.080 --> 31:36.160
Ms. Yu, please do not be so formal. Sit.

31:43.760 --> 31:46.600
Changyu spoke of you before.

31:47.120 --> 31:50.160
With the great battle approaching,
you would not have come

31:50.240 --> 31:51.840
unless it was something important.

31:53.800 --> 31:54.840
Indeed.

31:58.280 --> 31:59.400
Leave us.

32:04.080 --> 32:05.680
The eldest son of Prince Changxin,

32:06.360 --> 32:09.160
or rather, the former Crown Prince's son.

32:09.240 --> 32:11.400
How much do you know about him?

32:13.840 --> 32:15.360
Knowing him was nothing

32:15.440 --> 32:16.720
but a cursed entanglement.

32:17.560 --> 32:20.680
When he nearly drowned,
I pitied him and saved him

32:20.760 --> 32:22.200
by giving him breath

32:22.280 --> 32:23.560
mouth-to-mouth.

32:24.360 --> 32:25.760
I never thought that kindness

32:25.840 --> 32:28.160
-would bring all this trouble.
-Giving him breath…

32:32.080 --> 32:34.480
He possesses a tiger tally.

32:34.560 --> 32:37.120
He claims it proves
Prince Changxin intends to rebel.

32:38.160 --> 32:39.560
But as far as I know,

32:39.640 --> 32:42.080
Prince Changxin does not know
his true identity.

32:42.160 --> 32:43.520
A tiger tally?

32:46.880 --> 32:48.320
They're estranged.

32:48.920 --> 32:51.200
He harbors deep resentment
toward Prince Changxin.

32:51.280 --> 32:53.840
He has been plotting to force
Prince Changxin into rebellion,

32:53.920 --> 32:55.400
so he can seize the throne himself.

32:58.560 --> 33:00.360
No wonder he wanted Yu Bao'er dead.

33:01.600 --> 33:03.840
If he plans to seize the throne

33:03.920 --> 33:05.360
through Prince Changxin's rebellion,

33:06.880 --> 33:09.360
he would never allow
another rightful heir to remain alive.

33:10.880 --> 33:12.040
Thank you for telling me this.

33:12.120 --> 33:13.920
The situation is urgent.
I must take my leave.

33:15.200 --> 33:16.160
Farewell.

33:21.120 --> 33:22.280
Ms. Yu.

33:22.360 --> 33:25.720
What kind of technique
is that mouth-to-mouth breathing?

33:28.440 --> 33:31.240
It is only a folk remedy from my hometown.

33:31.320 --> 33:33.200
You breathe into the patient's mouth,

33:33.280 --> 33:34.720
then press on the chest.

33:34.800 --> 33:35.760
It can save a life.

33:36.720 --> 33:38.080
I see.

33:38.920 --> 33:41.200
It is also mentioned
in Treatise on Cold Damage.

33:42.040 --> 33:43.200
Though the method

33:43.280 --> 33:45.920
of mouth-to-mouth breathing
is somewhat different.

33:46.520 --> 33:49.200
Still, such contact between men and women
could be seen as improper.

33:54.400 --> 33:55.600
Your righteousness is admirable.

33:55.680 --> 33:56.960
I've learned much today. Farewell.

34:01.640 --> 34:02.880
Wenkan.

34:02.960 --> 34:05.440
Marquis Wu'an plans to lead
the main force of the Yanzhou army

34:05.520 --> 34:08.920
straight to Prince Changxin's
command camp in Luocheng.

34:10.320 --> 34:12.320
Luocheng is the prince's main base.

34:12.400 --> 34:13.639
It will be heavily guarded.

34:14.960 --> 34:16.840
How could the Marquis win
with so few troops?

34:17.440 --> 34:22.239
That is why I want you
to personally lead 3,000 elite soldiers.

34:23.360 --> 34:24.880
Split them into several detachments

34:25.480 --> 34:27.760
to cover the Marquis
while he strikes their command.

34:28.880 --> 34:31.280
Only then will we have a chance.

34:32.120 --> 34:33.360
But within Lucheng,

34:34.120 --> 34:35.600
if Yanzhou and Xie forces are gone,

34:35.679 --> 34:36.800
you've only got 5,000 men.

34:37.520 --> 34:40.199
Now you're giving me 3,000,
how will you hold up here in Lucheng?

34:40.280 --> 34:41.920
Even if all 5,000 stayed,

34:42.000 --> 34:44.960
do you think they could hold off
Prince Changxin's 50,000 troops?

34:46.040 --> 34:47.159
The battle for Lucheng

34:47.239 --> 34:49.239
must rely on an unexpected strike.

34:50.159 --> 34:51.000
Do not worry.

34:51.600 --> 34:52.520
Lucheng

34:53.360 --> 34:54.960
will not fall while I'm here.

34:58.000 --> 34:59.240
Zhenwei Commandant of Jizhou,

34:59.320 --> 35:00.440
Li Huai'an, accepts the order.

35:02.320 --> 35:04.560
It is such a relief
that Bao'er has been found.

35:04.640 --> 35:05.560
All thanks to Yan Zheng.

35:05.640 --> 35:07.760
I will never forget this kindness.

35:08.360 --> 35:09.520
Mrs. Fan,

35:09.600 --> 35:10.720
look who it is.

35:11.600 --> 35:12.640
Changyu.

35:12.720 --> 35:14.800
Kang Xiaodan! What are you doing here?

35:15.400 --> 35:16.760
Lord Li heard I was from Lin'an,

35:16.840 --> 35:18.200
so he told me to return with you.

35:20.080 --> 35:21.640
I also heard about my grandmother.

35:23.280 --> 35:24.800
Thank you for laying her to rest.

35:27.480 --> 35:29.640
We are all from Lin'an.
No need for thanks.

35:29.720 --> 35:31.720
Perfect timing. We can head back together.

35:37.680 --> 35:38.520
General,

35:39.360 --> 35:40.320
we are about to depart.

35:41.200 --> 35:42.560
I wish you a great victory.

35:42.640 --> 35:43.960
I will wait for your good news.

35:46.080 --> 35:47.040
If fate allows us to meet again,

35:47.680 --> 35:49.160
I hope you will answer my questions.

35:49.960 --> 35:53.160
If Heaven allows me to survive this battle
and stand with Lucheng,

35:53.240 --> 35:56.760
then I will tell you everything I know.

35:59.600 --> 36:00.560
Thank you.

36:02.800 --> 36:03.840
Let's go.

36:10.520 --> 36:12.720
Jingyuan, the northwest frontier is harsh.

36:12.800 --> 36:14.720
Jinzhou, Chongzhou, and Jizhou

36:14.800 --> 36:16.040
are especially barren.

36:16.120 --> 36:18.480
You must take care when you go there.

36:19.160 --> 36:22.200
A real man should earn
his merit in battle.

36:22.280 --> 36:24.040
That is far better

36:24.120 --> 36:25.680
than staying in the capital

36:25.760 --> 36:27.840
bowing and scraping
to flatter the powerful.

36:29.600 --> 36:32.760
A pity. I will not live
to see your son born.

36:32.840 --> 36:34.040
It will be a daughter.

36:34.120 --> 36:35.520
You prefer a girl?

36:37.040 --> 36:38.200
Jingyuan,

36:38.280 --> 36:39.800
you have read more books than I have.

36:39.880 --> 36:41.560
Help me give my daughter a name.

36:42.160 --> 36:45.280
Why not let your master name the child?

36:45.800 --> 36:47.600
He is too important.

36:47.680 --> 36:49.360
I fear it would overwhelm the child.

36:51.400 --> 36:53.440
Let me think.

36:53.960 --> 36:55.240
What name would suit her?

36:57.680 --> 36:58.680
Changyu.

36:59.280 --> 37:00.440
-Changyu?
-Yes.

37:01.880 --> 37:04.000
May she forever bask in her parents' love,

37:04.080 --> 37:06.400
like jade steps
fragrant with spring grass.

37:06.480 --> 37:07.480
What do you think?

37:08.480 --> 37:10.880
Excellent. That is a wonderful name.

37:13.320 --> 37:15.840
LUCHENG

37:15.920 --> 37:16.800
Qilin,

37:18.120 --> 37:20.600
you raised a fine daughter.

37:21.160 --> 37:24.480
Loyal, righteous, and fearless.

37:26.920 --> 37:29.040
I truly envy you.

37:57.040 --> 37:58.200
The longer the war drags on,

37:58.800 --> 38:01.200
the harder life becomes for the people.

38:01.800 --> 38:03.520
Starving bodies line the roads.

38:03.600 --> 38:05.360
Refugees wander from place to place.

38:06.120 --> 38:08.840
If a war can be ended quickly
with the fewest casualties,

38:08.920 --> 38:10.840
then even those who kill

38:11.360 --> 38:14.400
may still be doing the greater good.

38:23.920 --> 38:25.880
Our army has never had a female officer.

38:25.960 --> 38:29.520
I had this armor specially made for you.

38:33.520 --> 38:37.120
May it accompany you
as you earn glory and win great victories.

38:48.360 --> 38:51.440
The last time I felt this uneasy

38:52.920 --> 38:56.720
was 17 years ago, at Jinzhou.

39:04.680 --> 39:06.920
Beat the drums. Assemble the troops.

39:08.400 --> 39:11.200
-Beat the drums! Assemble the troops!
-Beat the drums! Assemble the troops!

39:20.240 --> 39:26.200
LUCHENG

39:35.840 --> 39:36.760
Off you go.

39:43.000 --> 39:43.840
Stop the carriage.

39:52.040 --> 39:54.320
Soldiers of the Jizhou army!

39:54.400 --> 39:55.360
Present!

39:56.040 --> 39:58.040
While the city stands, I stand!

39:58.120 --> 39:59.920
If the city falls, I fall with it!

40:00.000 --> 40:02.160
-While the city stands, we stand!
-While the city stands, we stand!

40:02.240 --> 40:04.240
-If the city falls, we fall with it!
-If the city falls, we fall with it!

40:17.320 --> 40:18.240
Qian.

40:19.720 --> 40:22.920
General Xie Qi
will escort you safely back to Lin'an,

40:23.480 --> 40:25.280
where you can reunite
with Ning and Bao'er.

40:26.160 --> 40:28.560
But I must stay. My fate is with Lucheng.

40:29.160 --> 40:30.120
Mrs. Fan,

40:30.800 --> 40:31.840
leave the battlefield to the Marquis.

40:32.440 --> 40:34.200
Trust in the Marquis
and the strategist's plans.

40:34.280 --> 40:35.440
They will surely hold Lucheng.

40:36.000 --> 40:38.360
Besides, Ning is still waiting
for you at home.

40:40.280 --> 40:41.240
I have seen battle.

40:42.480 --> 40:43.880
I know how terrifying war can be.

40:44.600 --> 40:45.840
But I also know

40:45.920 --> 40:47.440
that if Lucheng falls,

40:47.520 --> 40:48.640
Jizhou will be next.

40:49.440 --> 40:50.600
And if Jizhou falls,

40:50.680 --> 40:52.160
the rebels will storm the capital.

40:52.800 --> 40:54.160
When that happens, this vast world

40:54.880 --> 40:56.520
will have no place left for me to hide.

40:57.800 --> 40:59.480
Where would Ning hide?

41:01.600 --> 41:03.040
Where would the people

41:04.480 --> 41:06.040
of Lin'an hide?

41:07.320 --> 41:08.200
You have my support.

41:09.440 --> 41:12.000
You are the bravest
and most formidable woman I have ever met.

41:12.960 --> 41:14.120
If this is your choice,

41:15.280 --> 41:16.280
then stay.

41:17.840 --> 41:20.000
Do not worry about me.
Once I return to Lin'an,

41:20.800 --> 41:23.280
I will take care of Ning,
Mrs. Zhao, and the others.

41:23.360 --> 41:24.680
If you must go,

41:26.080 --> 41:27.080
then go without hesitation.

41:30.760 --> 41:32.520
Do not worry. We are going with her.

41:34.240 --> 41:35.160
Behind us,

41:36.920 --> 41:38.240
we have Lin'an to defend.

41:40.840 --> 41:41.920
Changyu.

41:42.440 --> 41:43.640
I will go with you.

41:43.720 --> 41:44.720
Count us in.

41:44.800 --> 41:45.720
We are coming too.

41:47.120 --> 41:49.480
Changyu, I used to be a coward.

41:50.200 --> 41:52.040
I only wanted to go home
to my grandmother.

41:52.840 --> 41:55.040
But she is gone now.
All I want is to avenge her.

41:55.640 --> 41:57.000
Changyu, you are not alone.

