I, Fan Changyu, swear this before you all.

42:13.200 --> 42:15.120
I will stand with Lucheng to the very end!

42:15.200 --> 42:16.160
-To the very end!
-To the very end!

42:16.240 --> 42:18.400
Defend Lucheng! Live or die with the city!

42:18.480 --> 42:20.960
Defend Lucheng! Live or die with the city!

42:21.040 --> 42:23.680
Defend Lucheng! Live or die with the city!

42:23.760 --> 42:26.520
